Gravatar CHANGES
================

Gravatar 0.2.2(2007-12-15T20:09:31+0800)
----------------------------------------
Added: readme.txt

Gravatar 0.2.1(2007-11-06T05:22:21+0800)
----------------------------------------
Added: zh_TW - Traditional Chinese locale

Gravatar 0.2 (2007-10-29T16:46:50+0800)
--------------------------
Added: Support using registered email as Gravatar email.
Added: Options page.
Added: Default image, Default role images, default size and rating options.
Added: Complete Deactivation.

Gravatar 0.1.3 (2007-10-28)
---------------------------
Moded: Show display_name instead of user_login if available.

Gravatar 0.1.2 (2007-10-23)
---------------------------
Fixed: Logic error in line 177 - || -> &&.
Moded: Use bb_random_pass.
Moded: Use gravatar_vcode to show human understandable message.
Added: Use bb_verify_mail.
Added: Allow entering Gravatar Email at resistration stage.

Gravatar 0.1.1 (2007-10-21)
---------------------------
Fixed: No gravatar_email results no avatar

Gravatar 0.1 (2007-10-20)
